<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Registration</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/main.css" />
    <!--Font Awesome-->
    <link href="https://pro.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.10.0/css/all.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body>
    <div id="app">
        <div class="container">
            <div v-if="step == '1'" class="step step1">
                <div class="logo d-flex mt-3">
                    <img src="./img/logoMain.png" alt="logo" />
                </div>
                <form method="get" action="/register">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <h3 class="welcome">Welcome, Prospective Students.</h3>
                        <p class="pr-font">We are genueinely happy you're here.</p>
                        <p class="pr-font">
                            Lagos Metropolitan Institute of Technology, Yaba (Est. 2020) is a Non-Degree
                            Engineering-Focused training School. Our Diploma Certificates are issued autonomously. We
                            pride ourself in our training process, the quality of our staff and graduates.
                        </p>

                        <p class="mt-3 pr-font">
                            <strong>Courses offered include?</strong>
                        <ul class="pr-font">
                            <li>Diploma in Software Engineering (1 year)</li>
                        </ul>

                        <span class="pr-font">
                            Propelled by the sense of responsibility to raise engineers seasoned by training & industry
                            experience; our curriculum features intensive academic and vocation approach.
                        </span>
                        </p>

                        <div class="mt-3">
                            <span class="pr-font d-flex align-items-center">
                                <input v-model="readTermsAndCondition" required class="accept-terms" type="checkbox" />
                                <span>I've read and understood what <b>LMIT</b> offers.</span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-row w-100 justify-content-end">
                        <button :disabled="!readTermsAndCondition" type="submit" class="btn-action btn-get-started">
                            Continue &nbsp; <i class="fal fa-long-arrow-right fa-lg"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue@2/dist/vue.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/c8c9028de4.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>